{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were volunteers to, to work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they came, and they said, no rides.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You don't go to your normal work, which at that time was still in Rothschwaige.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You go out to the central bus-- central railway station in Munich-- Hauptbahnhof-- and they will give you the instructions there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the roads were cut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fire brigades were-- pipes all over the streets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Streets were closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these French drivers, they only had the-- they knew-- only knew the main roads, which were blocked.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And each truck were open trucks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were about 20 on the truck with stools and had chalk numbers, from one to about 20 trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had to remember the trucks, in case there is another alarm, so we know which truck we came to disappear from the area.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The weekend, I was already-- from 7:00-- three hours it took them to get to the Hauptbahnof.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was only 10 kilometers away from Allach, from, from the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rothschwaige was only three kilometers from Allach, same area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And first-- after the first night bombing, which was a British bombing, the railway was completely scattered-- trucks with axles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the hood was all glass, the main hood on the-- on the station, all broken with bits of things flying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Road-- wheels, you could see on the rooftops.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we found, yeah, the German command in the area of the railway station, one of the foremen, or whoever it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, you can eat and drink whatever you find here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But don't take anything with you-- same old story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what we found is burning local materials full of tobacco from Hungary and shoes from Romania.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we couldn't touch the shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
